20weather%20office%20has%20predicted%20more%20showers%20for%20the%20national%20capital%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELight%20rain%20pounded%20several%20parts%20of%20Delhi%20yesterday%20as%20well.%C2%A0In%20the%20case%20of%20more%20rain%20in%20Delhi%2C%20experts%20say%2C%20the%20rainwater%20may%20overflow%20and%20take%20longer%20than%20usual%20to%20drain%20out.%20Waterlogging%20could%20worsen%20the%20situation%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20breaching%20a%2045-year%20record%2C%20the%20Yamuna%20which%20runs%20through%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20came%20down%20to%20207.68%20metres%20this%20morning%20even%20as%20several%20areas%20in%20Delhi%20remained%20flooded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20river%20had%20reached%20208.66%20meters%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20surpassing%20the%20previous%20high%20of%20207.49%20meters%20in%201978.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20and%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20were%20called%20in%20as%20the%20water%20submerged%20key%20areas%20of%20central%20Delhi%2C%20including%20ITO%20and%20Rajghat.%20The%20road%20outside%20Hanuman%20Mandir%2C%20Yamuna%20Bazar%2C%20Geeta%20Colony%2C%20Civil%20Lines%20are%20also%20heavily%20waterlogged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floodwaters%20even%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20some%20crematoriums%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20Nigam%20Bodh%20Ghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20boys%20drowned%20while%20trying%20to%20swim%20in%20the%20floodwaters%20in%20northwest%20Delhi's%20Mukundpur%20Chowk%20area.%20These%20were%20the%20first%20deaths%20reported%20in%20the%20city%20since%20the%20Yamuna%20water%20crossed%20the%20danger%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20last%20evening%20said%20the%20work%20is%20on%20to%20open%20the%20five%20gates%20of%20Yamuna%20Barrage%20so%20that%20the%20water%20flows%20back%20to%20the%20barrage.%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20jammed%20gate%20of%20the%20ITO%20Barrage%20has%20been%20opened.%20Soon%20all%20the%20five%20gates%20will%20be%20opened%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20will%20be%20normal%20soon%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20if%20it%20doesn't%20rain.%20If%20it%20rains%2C%20then%20it%20may%20take%20a%20bit%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20roads%20turned%20into%20little%20rivers%2C%20the%20authorities%20continued%20the%20rescue%20work.%20Dogs%20and%20cattle%20were%20also%20among%20the%20evacuees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20task%20forces%20are%20also%20being%20moved%20from%20Meerut%20to%20Delhi%2C%20and%20will%20be%20kept%20on%20stand%20by%20to%20deal%20with%20contingencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%204%2C500%20traffic%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20affected%20areas%20to%20decongest%20traffic%20and%20help%20commuters%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20the%20traffic%20restrictions%20will%20be%20lifted%20depending%20on%20how%20fast%20the%20water%20recedes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20on%20Thursday%20directed%20that%20non-essential%20government%20offices%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20colleges%20be%20closed%20till%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20government%20has%20banned%20the%20entry%20of%20heavy%20goods%20vehicles%2C%20barring%20those%20carrying%20essential%20items%2C%20into%20the%20city%20from%20the%20four%20borders%2C%20including%20Singhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689393420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fmfbf02m8_delhi-rain_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-floods-delhi-rain-yamuna-river-amid-flood-chaos-rain-thundershowers-prediction-for-delhi-today-4209209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Delhi%20battles%20with%20severe%20flooding%20after%20the%20record%20rain%2C%20and%20the%20release%20of%20water%20from%20Hathni%20Kund%20Barrage%20in%20Haryana%20swelled%20water%20levels%20in%20the%20Yamuna%2C%20the%20weather%20office%20has%20predicted%20more%20showers%2