%20for%20the%20Nothing%20Phone's%20first%20pop-up%20in%20the%20US%20at%209%20a.m.%2C%2010%20hours%20before%20it%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20OnePlus%208T%20user%20wasn't%20here%20for%20the%20company's%20new%20release%2C%20dubbed%20Phone%20(2).%20He%20was%20just%20here%20to%20show%20his%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20first%20launch%20in%20the%20US%20for%20Nothing.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20product%20for%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Hernandez%20says.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20a%20new%20design%2C%20new%20everything%2C%20new%20language%2C%20new%20community%2C%20new%20support%20and%20everything%20just%20feels%20fresh.%20It%20feels%20like%20the%20excitement%20of%20new%20technology%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20was%20founded%20by%20Carl%20Pei%2C%20who%20co-founded%20OnePlus%2C%20which%20makes%20quality%20phones%20with%20top%20specs%20at%20affordable%20prices.%20Pei%20started%20Nothing%20in%202020%20in%20London%20with%20big%20ambitions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20technology%20and%20design%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20released%20the%20Nothing%20Phone%20(1)%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2013%2C%20for%20the%20US%20debut%20of%20the%20Phone%20(2)%2C%20Pei%20was%20inside%20a%20red%20bubble-shaped%20pop-up%20kiosk%20in%20Manhattan's%20Meatpacking%20District%2C%20where%20he%20greeted%20customers%2C%20checked%20receipts%20and%20bagged%20orders.%20He%20talked%20with%20several%20of%20them%20in%20English%20and%20Mandarin%2C%20shaking%20hands%2C%20taking%20selfies%20and%20autographing%20their%20packages%20on%20request.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20introducing%20the%20Phone%20(2)%20with%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bglyph%20interface%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20back%2C%20Nothing%20aims%20to%20help%20users%20minimize%20screen%20interactions%20by%20accessing%20key%20information%20at%20a%20glance.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20order%20an%20Uber%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20the%20interface%20to%20act%20as%20a%20progress%20tracker%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20watch%20the%20lights%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20phone%20count%20down%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20driver%20without%20having%20to%20look%20at%20the%20screen%20in%20the%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20when%20I%20unlock%20my%20phone%2C%20I%20just%20fall%20into%20the%20social%20media%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%20Pei%20says%20while%20at%20at%20the%20pop-up%20event.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20like%20me.%20How%20can%20we%20empower%20them%20to%20open%20the%20screen%20a%20little%20bit%20less%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glyph%20lights%20were%20embraced%20by%20the%20on-site%20customers.%20%26quot%3BInnovations%20can%20look%20like%20gimmicks%20when%20something%20innovative%20is%20starting%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rushna%20Quddus%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20in%20chemistry%20at%20New%20York%20University.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20why%20that%20doesn't%20look%20like%20a%20gimmick%20to%20me%20is%20because%20someone%20bothered%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20of%20'What%20about%20behind%20the%20phone%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20leaving%20that%20useless%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%2C%20which%20runs%20on%20Android%2C%20has%20a%206.7-inch%20screen-roughly%20similar%20to%20the%20iPhone%2014%20Pro%20Max-and%20up%20to%20512%20gigabytes%20of%20storage.%20Other%20than%20the%20lights%20on%20the%20back%2C%20the%20biggest%20difference%20between%20a%20Nothing%20Phone(2)%20and%20other%20Android%20models%20is%20the%20Nothing%20OS%202.0%2C%20the%20software%20based%20on%20Android%2013%2C%20which%20allows%20users%20to%20tailor%20everything%20from%20app%20labels%20and%20grid%20design%20to%20widget%20size%20and%20color%20themes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHenry%20Tom%2C%20a%20user-experience%20designer%20working%20at%20a%20Wall%20Street%20bank%2C%20decided%20to%20sell%20his%20iPhone%2014%20Pro%20Max%20after%20buying%20a%20white%20Phone%20(2)%20at%20the%20pop-up.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20talk%20about%20the%20vision%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20in%20their%20vision%20of%20making%20phones%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20really%20missing%20in%20this%20industry%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPei%20says%20that's%20exactly%20the%20point.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20targeting%20young%20and%20creative%20people.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20our%20users%2C%20they're%20very%20interested%20in%20new%20technology%20and%20also%20interested%20in%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20For%20its%20worldwide%20premiere%20on%20July%2011%20he%20showed%20up%20in%20a%20vlog-style%20debut%20video%20with%20YouTuber%20Casey%20Neistat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Apple%20and%20Samsung%2C%20they%20have%20a%20very%20good%20business%20model%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20Pei%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20They%20know%20who%20their%20customers%20are.%20So%20why%20take%20a%20big%20risk%20on%20the%20product%20side%3F%20I%20think%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20years%20that%20a%20small%20team%20with%20big%20ambitions%20is%20able%20to%20chart%20a%20slightly%20different%20course%20to%20where%20the%20smartphone%20industry%20and%20consumer%20tech%20as%20a%20whole%20can%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Phone%20(2)%20starts%20at%20%24599%20and%20has%20full%20band%20support%20for%20AT%26amp%3BT%20and%20T-Mobile%20and%20what%20Nothing%20is%20calling%20%26quot%3Blimited%20support%26quot%3B%20for%20Verizon.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20phones%20are%20available%20for%20purchase%20only%20on%20the%20Nothing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689390300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fj18n5mcg_carl-pei-ceo-of-nothing-phone-bloomberg-_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-600-device-rethinks-how-the-back-of-your-smar