ual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-smoking-cigarette_6219189.jpg%3F20230715035722%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhong-kongers-urged-to-stare-at-smokers-in-a-disapproving-way-to-help-create-a-tobacco-free-city-12921254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20should%20stare%20at%20smokers%20disapprovingly%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%20tobacco-free%20city%2C%20the%20territory's%20health%20minister%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhong-kongers-urged-to-stare-at-smokers-in-a-disapproving-way-to-help-create-a-tobacco-free-city-12921254%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhong-kongers-urged-to-stare-at-smokers-in-a-disapproving-way-to-help-create-a-tobacco-free-city-12921254%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhong-kongers-urged-to-stare-at-smokers-in-a-disapproving-way-to-help-create-a-tobacco-free-city-12921254%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Prime%20Objectives%20After%20Landing%20On%20The%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Chandrayaan%203%20mission%20was%20launched%20on%20Friday%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20landing%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20a%20feat%20that%20has%20only%20been%20achieved%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20%3C%2Fa%3Espacecraft%20will%20reach%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20about%20a%20month%20after%20its%20launch.%20The%20lander%2C%20Vikram%2C%20and%20the%20rover%2C%20Pragyaan%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20main%20objectives%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20was%20launched%20into%20space%20by%20the%20LVM3%20rocket%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Sriharikota.%20Once%20in%20orbit%2C%20the%20propulsion%20module%20will%20carry%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20configuration%20to%20a%20100-kilometre%20lunar%20orbit.%20The%20lander%20will%20then%20separate%20from%20the%20propulsion%20module%20and%20attempt%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20propulsion%20module%20also%20carries%20the%20Spectro-polarimetry%20of%20Habitable%20Planet%20Earth%20(SHAPE)%20payload%2C%20which%20will%20analyse%20the%20light%20from%20Earth%20to%20study%20its%20spectral%20and%20polarimetric%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20a%20follow-up%20mission%20to%20Chandrayaan-2%20that%20will%20attempt%20to%20land%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20moon%20and%20deploy%20a%20rover%20to%20explore%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20The%20rover%20will%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20composition%20and%20geology%20of%20the%20moon%2C%20which%20will%20help%20scientists%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20history%20and%20evolution%20of%20our%20nearest%20celestial%20neighbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20ISRO%20Chairman%20S%20Somanath%20discussed%20how%20the%20space%20agency%20has%20learned%20from%20its%20past%20failures%20and%20implemented%20changes%20to%20improve%20the%20chances%20of%20success%20for%20the%20%C2%A0Chandrayaan-3%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20lacuna%20in%20the%20last%20Chandrayaa-2%20mission%20was%20that%20there%20were%20off-nominal%20conditions%20that%20were%20initiated%20in%20the%20system.%20Everything%20was%20not%20nominal.%20And%20the%20craft%20was%20not%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20off-nominal%20condition%20for%20a%20safe%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22as59cle%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fas59cle_chandrayaan-3_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20primary%20goal%20of%20landing%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20Chandrayaan-3%20will%20also%20conduct%20scientific%20experiments%20to%20study%20the%20moon's%20environment%2C%20including%20its%20history%2C%20geology%2C%20and%20potential%20for%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20carrying%20six%20payloads%20to%20study%20the%20lunar%20soil%20and%20capture%20photographs%20of%20Earth%20from%20the%20lunar%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%2014-day%20mission%20(one%20Lunar%20day)%20upon%20landing%2C%20Chandrayaan-3%20will%20conduct%20a%20series%20of%20groundbreaking%20experiments%20using%20its%20payloads%20RAMBHA%20and%20ILSA.%20These%20experiments%20will%20study%20the%20moon's%20atmosphere%20and%20dig%20into%20the%20surface%20to%20better%20understand%20its%20mineral%20composition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20Vikram%20will%20photograph%20the%20rover%20Pragyaan%20which%20will%20deploy%20its%20instruments%20to%20study%20seismic%20activity%20on%20the%20moon.%20Pragyaan%20will%20use%20its%20laser%20beams%20to%20melt%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20called%20regolith%2C%20and%20analsze%20the%20gases%20emitted%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20mission%2C%20India%20will%20not%20only%20access%20a%20wealth%20of%20knowledge%20about%20the%20lunar%20surface%20but%20also%20its%20potential%20for%20human%20habitation%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chief%20S%20Somnath%20said%20that%20a%20location%20near%20the%20equator%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20suitable%20for%20human%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20that%20aspect%20very%20well%20-%20which%20is%20the%20best%20place%20for%20human%20beings%20to%20go.%20You%20are%20talking%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20availability%20of%20water%20and%20that%20is%20possibly%20one%20aspect.%20Today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20important%20requirements%20is%20temperature%20excursions%20(deviations)%20as%20well%20as%20availability%20of%20solar%20power%20for%20power%20generation.%20From%20that%20point%2C%20an%20equatorial%20location%20could%20be%20more%20ideal%20for%20human%20beings%20to%20settle%2C%20if%20at%20all%20a%20human%20habitat%20has%20to%20be%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22vg42q5g8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvg42q5g8_chandrayaan-3_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20payload%2C%20the%20Radio%20Anatomy%20of%20Moon%20Bound%20Hypersensitive%20Ionosphere%20and%20Atmosphere%20(RAMBHA)%2C%20will%20measure%20the%20density%20of%20charged%20particles%20near%20the%20lunar%20surface%20and%20how%20it%20changes%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Alpha%20Particle%20X-Ray%20Spectrometer%20(APXS)%20will%20measure%20the%20chemical%20composition%20and%20infer%20the%20mineralogical%20composition%20of%20the%20moon's%20surface%20while%20the%20Laser-Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscope%20(LIBS)%20will%20determine%20the%20elemental%20composition%20of%20lunar%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20the%20moon's%20frigid%20night%20temperatures%20of%20-232%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20Chandrayaan-3%20will%20send%20its%20lunar%20lander%20to%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20at%2070%20degrees%20latitude%20before%20nightfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20will%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20at%205%3A47%20pm%20on%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689387780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F1v9gear_chandrayaan3_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-isro-explained-chandrayaan-3s-prime-objectives-after-landing-on-the-moon-4209226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Chandrayaan%203%20missio