msid-101770924%2Cimgsize-1174434.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fdoctors-remove-two-inch-nail-from-mans-head%2Farticleshow%2F101770889.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20six-hour%20surgery%2C%20doctors%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20successfully%20removed%20a%20two-inch%20nail%20from%20inside%20the%20head%20of%20a%2023-year-old%20factory%20worker.%20The%20nail%20had%20got%20in%20when%20a%20co-worker's%20nail%20gun%20had%20accidentally%20recoiled.%20Doctors%20drilled%20into%20the%20man's%20head%20to%20remove%20the%20metal%20and%20two%20days%20later%2C%20on%20July%206%2C%20Brahma%20of%20Machhali%20Gaon%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20was%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital.%20The%20very%20next%20day%20he%20walked%20into%20the%20conference%20room%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20smiling%20at%20the%20flashing%20media%20cameras.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fdoctors-remove-two-inch-nail-from-mans-head%2Farticleshow%2F101770889.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20Replay%20of%20Fake%20PMO%20Official%20Episode%2C%20UP%20Engineer%20Arrested%20for%20Posing%20as%20OSD%20to%20Amit%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14214617%2F20230709131L.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20the%20conman%20caught%20who%20faked%20as%20a%20senior%20PMO%20official%20before%20being%20caught%20last%20year%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20can%20be%20called%20a%20replay%20of%20the%20same%20modus%20operandi%2C%20a%20civil%20engineer%2C%20currently%20unemployed%2C%20was%20caught%20allegedly%20impersonating%20as%20an%20Officer-on-Special-Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Amit%20Shah.%20Identified%20as%20Robin%20Upadhyay%2C%2048%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Meerut%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20accused%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20a%20professional%20working%20with%20various%20multinational%20companies%20for%20over%2025%20years%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Upadhyay%20was%20eying%20the%20post%20of%20Vice%20President-cum-Project%20Coordinator%20for%20the%20Ganga%20Expressway%20project.%20The%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20one%20Akshat%20Sharma%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Cyber%20Police%20Station%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Sharma%20reported%20having%20received%20an%20email%20on%20his%20official%20ID%20from%20a%20seemingly%20fraudulent%20email%20address%2C%20allegedly%20belonging%20to%20Rajeev%20Kumar%2C%20the%20OSD%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister.%20In%20the%20email%2C%20the%20impersonator%20instructed%20Sharma%20to%20ensure%20Upadhyay%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20the%20Senior%20Associate%20Vice%20President-cum-Project%20Coordinator%20for%20the%20Ganga%20Expressway%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkiran-patel-fake-pmo-official-profile%5C%22%3EThe%20Story%20of%20the%20Fake%20PMO%20Official%20Who%20Took%20the%20Government%20for%20a%20Ride%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20probe%2C%20the%20police%20found%20the%20email%20ID%2C%20rajeev.osd.mha%40gmail.com%2C%20was%20a%20sham%20account%20created%20solely%20for%20deceiving%20individuals.%20Through%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20the%20police%20team%20successfully%20identified%20the%20prime%20suspect%2C%20Robin%20Upadhyay.%20Further%20analysis%20revealed%20that%20the%20email%20had%20been%20created%20six%20to%20seven%20days%20prior%20and%20was%20registered%20under%20Upadhyay%E2%80%99s%20name.%20Acting%20swiftly%2C%20the%20authorities%20traced%20and%20detained%20Upadhyay%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Meerut%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20Hemant%20Tiwari%2C%20Additional%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interrogation%2C%20Upadhyay%20confessed%20to%20his%20crime.%20He%20said%20being%20a%20civil%20engineer%2C%20he%20possessed%20extensive%20experience%20in%20civil%20construction%20projects%20and%20researched%20ongoing%20highway%20projects%20and%20their%20progress%20to%20find%20a%20place%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20incident%20follows%20a%20similar%20occurrence%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20where%20Kiran%20Patel%20from%20Gujarat%20was%20apprehended%20for%20impersonating%20a%20senior%20official%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO).%20Patel%20had%20successfully%20deceived%20officials%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20availing%20himself%20of%20Z%20Plus%20security%20and%20other%20privileges.%20In%20a%20more%20recent%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fgujarat-vadodara-resident-arrested-posing-pmo-official-8683956%2F%5C%22%3EMayank%20Tiwari%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20was%20arrested%20for%20posing%20as%20a%20PMO%20official%2C%20attempting%20to%20secure%20admission%20for%20two%20children%20in%20a%20private%20school%20and%20swindling%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20money%20from%20the%20school%20using%20his%20fake%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F20161226%2FFotoJet-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F20161226%2FFotoJet-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F20161226%2FFotoJet-2-300x123.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3