Cp%3ETaking%20to%20Twitter%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20said%20that%20as%20per%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20(CWC)%20guidelines%2C%20water%20with%20a%20flow%20of%20over%201%20lakh%20cusecs%20cannot%20be%20discharged%20into%20Western%20Yamuna%20and%20Eastern%20Yamuna%20Canal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetired%20IAS%20and%20Advisor%20(Irrigation)%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Haryana%20Devendra%20Singh%20said%20that%20as%20per%20CWC%20guidelines%2C%20if%20the%20water%20flow%20in%20Hathini%20Kund%20barrage%20is%20more%20than%201%20lakh%20cusecs%2C%20the%20water%20will%20flow%20into%20Western%20Yamuna%20and%20Eastern%20Yamuna%20Canal%20due%20to%20large%20boulders%20cannot%20be%20discharged%2C%26quot%3B%20DIPR%20Haryana%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20may%20damage%20the%20barrage%20structures%2C%20so%20the%20head%20regulator%20gates%20of%20the%20canals%20are%20closed%20and%20the%20cross%20regulator%20gates%20at%20the%20barrage%20are%20opened%20for%20free%20flow%20of%20water%20into%20Yamuna%20river%2C%26quot%3B%20DIPR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20taking%20any%20name%2C%20DIPR%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLeaders%20of%20a%20political%20party%20today%20alleged%20through%20a%20video%20on%20social%20media%20that%20water%20is%20being%20released%20from%20Hathini%20Kund%20Barrage%20into%20the%20Yamuna%20River%20by%20not%20releasing%20water%20into%20the%20Western%20Yamuna%20Canal%20and%20Eastern%20Yamuna%20Canal%2C%20causing%20floods%20in%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Devendra%20Singh)%20said%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20unusual%20in%20this%20case%20also%20and%20unnecessary%20controversy%20is%20being%20created%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20hide%20its%20negligence%2Finefficiency%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20flood%20preparedness%2C%26quot%3B%20DIPR%20Haryana%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20AAP%20chief%20spokesperson%2C%20Priyanka%20Kakkar%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20case%20of%20a%20flood%2C%20water%20is%20released%20from%20Hathni%20Kund%20towards%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%20in%20balanced%20quantities.%20But%20from%20July%209%20to%2013%2C%20all%20the%20water%20was%20released%20towards%20Delhi.%20Had%20water%20been%20released%20equally%20towards%20all%20the%20three%20states%2C%20the%20areas%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Yamuna%20would%20have%20been%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%20listed%20out%20the%20five%20states%20that%20are%20the%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20floods%20in%20the%20country%20and%20pointed%20out%20how%20Delhi%20is%20included%20in%20this%20list%20despite%20there%20being%20no%20rainfall%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20five%20states%20within%20the%20country%2C%20that%20are%20facing%20the%20brunt%20of%20natural%20calamity%20at%20the%20moment%20-%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Delhi.%20If%20we%20speak%20only%20about%20Delhi%2C%20everyone%20here%20will%20be%20aware%20that%20it%20hasn't%20rained%20in%20the%20city%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days.%20Then%20why%20is%20it%20still%20that%20the%20water%20level%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20has%20constantly%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20flood%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20that%20are%20in%20the%20low-lying%20region%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20providing%20details%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20water%20from%20the%20Hathnikund%20barrage%20was%20intentionally%20only%20being%20sent%20to%20Delhi%20to%20flood%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20Hathnikund%20barrage%2C%20there%20are%20three%20different%20routes%20that%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20takes.%20One%20stream%20brings%20the%20water%20into%20Delhi%2C%20another%20takes%20it%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20the%20final%20stream%20takes%20the%20water%20into%20Haryana.%20Ideally%2C%20in%20a%20flood%20such%20as%20this%20one%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20ideal%20if%20the%20water%20pressure%20was%20equally%20distributed%20into%20the%20three%20canals.%20But%20the%20BJP%20conspired%20to%20send%20all%20of%20the%20water%20into%20the%20stream%20that%20forms%20the%20Yamuna%20River%20and%20enters%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689381780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fcgvugalg_delhi-flood-ani_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-floods-aap-alleges-haryana-intentionally-diverting-water-towards-delhi-4209187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20alleged%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20the%20Haryana%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%26quot%3B%20divert%20water%20towards%20flood-hit%20Delhi%20through%20Hathnikund%20Barrage%2C%20the%20state%20government%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20the%20AAP's%20claims%20were%20'misleading'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-floods-aap-alleges-haryana-intentionally-diverting-water-towards-delhi-4209187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-floods-aap-alleges-haryana-intentionally-diverting-water-towards-delhi-4209187%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-floods-aap-alleges-haryana-intentionally-diverting-water-towards-delhi-4209187%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Film%20Academy%E2