0and%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%26quot%3BTitanic%26quot%3B%20star%20Frances%20Fisher%2C%2071.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20standing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%2C%20yards%20award%20from%20the%20historic%20arched%20entryway%20to%20Paramount%20Picture%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChanting%20writers%20welcomed%20the%20new%20influx%20of%20noticeably%20louder%20voices%20from%20the%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20(SAG-AFTRA)%2C%20and%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20arrival%20of%20globally%20recognizable%20faces%20should%20bring%20renewed%20attention%20to%20the%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStars%20including%20Allison%20Janney%20(%26quot%3BThe%20West%20Wing%26quot%3B)%2C%20Mandy%20Moore%20(%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Us%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20Ben%20Schwartz%20(%26quot%3BSonic%20the%20Hedgehog%26quot%3B)%20joined%20rank-and-file%20actors%20on%20the%20picket%20lines%2C%20while%20Jason%20Sudeikis%20and%20Susan%20Sarandon%20showed%20up%20across%20the%20country%20at%20protests%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20historic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zev%20Frank%2C%2036%2C%20a%20writer%20on%20Amazon%20Prime%20series%20%26quot%3BPatriot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20see%20them%20show%20up%20like%20this%2C%20in%20huge%20numbers%2C%20it%20feels%20different%20today.%20It%20feels%20electric.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20part%20of%20an%20industry%20that%20has%20so%20many%20people%20that%20are%20front-facing%2C%20so%20that%20extra%20PR%20is%20gonna%20be%20helpful%2C%20said%20Tien%20Tran%2C%2036%2C%20star%20of%20sitcom%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Met%20Your%20Father.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Disgusting'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20demands%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20is%20asking%20studios%20for%20pay%20rises%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20inflation%2C%20a%20greater%20share%20in%20the%20profit%20of%20hit%20shows%20or%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20proposals%20were%20dismissed%20by%20Disney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20this%20week%20as%20%26quot%3Bunrealistic%26quot%3B%20--%20comments%20that%20invoked%20fury%20among%20several%20strikers%20interviewed%20by%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20refurnishing%20his%20house%20right%20now%20for%20%245%20million%2C%20and%20these%20people%20don't%20even%20have%20health%20insurance...%20it's%20disrespectful%20and%20disgusting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shawn%20Richardz%2C%20an%20actress%20who%20has%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3BTreme%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BNip%2FTuck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20guy%20is%20saying%20we're%20asking%20for%20unrealistic%20things%3F%20Are%20you%20kidding%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20really%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20people%20on%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20agreed%20actor%20E.J.%20Arriola%2042.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20artists%2C%20we've%20been%20around%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20there%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20sort%20of%20respect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20heaped%20praised%20on%20SAG-AFTRA%20president%20Fran%20Drescher%2C%20whose%20similar%20language%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20announcing%20the%20strike%20Thursday%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20swarmed%20by%20fellow%20actors%20outside%20Netflix%20on%20Friday%2C%20as%20the%20crowd%20cheered%20her%20comments%20and%20took%20them%20up%20as%20chants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20among%20the%20hundreds%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%20and%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20signs%2C%20placards%20from%20other%20Hollywood%20unions%20representing%20behind-the%20scenes%20crew%20and%20transport%20workers%20were%20visible%20among%20the%20marchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20sets%20to%20build%20without%20actors%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20those%20guilds%20re-negotiate%20their%20own%20contracts%20with%20studios%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20