C%20at%20whim%2C%20vanish%20altogether.%20And%20unfortunately%20for%20some%20investors%2C%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20has%20happened%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202023%20has%20seen%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20illicit%20schemes%20that%20fraudsters%20have%20used%20to%20pilfer%20vast%20sums%20of%20money%20from%20the%20financial%20system.%20Detailed%20below%20are%20three%20of%20the%20oddest%20scandals%20to%20have%20befuddled%20the%20financial%20system%20in%20recent%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20of%20the%20missing%20silver%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20a%20vault%20where%20a%20precious%20metals%20dealer%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20storing%20over%20half%20a%20million%20of%20his%20clients'%20silver%20coins%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fcommodities-metals-silver-coins-vanished-cftc-fraud-dealer-fined-146m-2023-7%5C%22%3Ewas%20little%20more%20than%20a%20bunch%20of%20paper%20IOUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20eight%20years%2C%20Robert%20Leroy%20Higgins%20had%20claimed%20he%20was%20safeguarding%20over%20%24110%20million%20of%20rare%20American%20Eagle%20silver%20coins%20through%20his%20two%20companies%2C%20Argent%20Asset%20Group%20LLC%20and%20First%20State%20Depository%20Company%20LLC%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20was%20found%20by%20courts%20to%20have%20fabricated%20the%20entire%20affair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CFTC%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfraudulent%20and%20deceptive%20scheme%26quot%3B%20and%20Higgins%20has%20since%20been%20ordered%20to%20repay%20%24113%20million%20to%20customers%20and%20%2433%20million%20in%20penalties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBurglary%20on%20the%20blockchain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Zhaojun%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20Multichain%2C%20went%20incommunicado%20in%20late%20May%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20disappearance%20of%20%24126%20million%20of%20locked%20token%20deposits%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D