ry%20is%20also%20in%20the%20business%20of%20what's%20called%20enhanced%20oil%20recovery%2C%20which%20involves%20using%20carbon%20dioxide%20to%20collect%20more%20oil%20from%20wells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExxon's%20move%20follows%20the%20passage%20last%20year%20of%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20which%20includes%20tax%20breaks%20for%20companies%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fexxon-mobil-denbury-carbon-capture-acquisition-e88462a294693e4139b24d6030ac3c2d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapture%20and%20store%20carbon%20dioxide%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20injecting%20new%20life%20into%20the%20nascent%20and%20controversial%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IRA%20is%20set%20to%20pump%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.democrats.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Finflation_reduction_act_one_page_summary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealmost%20%24370%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20a%20decade%20into%20a%20range%20of%20efforts%20to%20help%20fight%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20put%20the%20US%20on%20a%20path%20to%20slash%20carbon%20emissions%20by%2040%25%20by%202030%2C%20a%20goal%20set%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20carbon%20capture%2C%20utilization%2C%20and%20storage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarbon%20capture%2C%20utilization%2C%20and%20storage%2C%20or%20CCUS%2C%20refers%20to%20technologies%20that%20trap%20carbon-dioxide%20emissions%2C%C2%A0often%20from%20large%20industrial%20sources%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fenergy-system%2Fcarbon-capture-utilisation-and-storage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epower%20plants%20or%20factories%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20being%20captured%20today%20is%20used%20to%20pump%20more%20oil%20from%20wells%2C%20a%20process%20known%20as%20enhanced%20oil%20recovery%2C%20or%20to%20make%20fertilizer.%20The%20gas%20can%20also%20be%20piped%20underground%20into%20geological%20formations%2C%20including%20oil-and-gas%20reservoirs%20or%20salty%20aquifers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20Exxon%20buying%20Denbury%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenbury%20gets%20most%20of%20its%20revenue%20from%20enhanced%20oil%20recovery%2C%20a%20technique%20that%20Exxon%20has%20a%20long%20record%20of%20using.%20But%20for%20Exxon%2C%20the%20acquisition%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fglobal%2Ffiles%2Fadvancing-climate-solutions-progress-report%2F2023%2F2023-advancing-climate-solutions-progress-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epart%20of%20a%20larger%20strategy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stay%20profitable%20as%20countries%20try%20to%20meet%20global%20climate%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20diversifying%20into%20producing%20solar%20and%20wind%20power%2C%20Exxon%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fdelivering-industrial-solutions%2Fcarbon-capture-and-storage%2Fccs-in-action%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eis%20betting%20that%20it%20can%20keep%20pumping%20oil%20and%20gas%20so%20long%20as%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20caps%20emissions%20flowing%20out%20of%20smokestacks%20at%20power%20plants%20and%20factories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20that%20captured%20CO2%20could%20be%20put%20to%20use%20by%20other%20industries%2C%20including%20makers%20of%20fertilizers%20and%20other%20chemicals.%20Most%20of%20the%20captured%20carbon%20dioxide%20will%20likely%20be%20stored%20underground%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IEA%20estimates%20that%20if%20the%20world%20achieves%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202050%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fenergy-system%2Fcarbon-capture-utilisation-and-storage%2Fco2-capture-and-utilisation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eless%20than%205%25%20of%20the%20carbon%20captured%20would%20be%20used%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20would%20need%20to%20be%20stored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransporting%20CO2%20requires%20pipelines%2C%20and%20Denbury%20has%201%2C300%20miles%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20pipelines%3B%20much%20of%20its%20network%20spans%20Louisiana%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20Mississippi.%20Denbury%20also%20already%20has%2010%20sites%20where%20it%20stores%20carbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purchase%20would%20help%20Exxon%20go%20deeper%20into%20this%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20able%20to%20acquire%20a%20really%20significant%20piece%20of%20existing%20infrastructure%2C%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20move%20much%20more%20quickly%20than%20if%20we%20were%20to%20try%20and%20build%20and%20replicate%20that%20infrastructure%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Ammann%2C%20president%20of%20Exxon's%20Low%20Carbon%20Solutions%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstatus%2F1679508792512327686%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20Bloomberg%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20with%20Denbury%20is%20one%20of%20several%20carbon-capture%20and%20storage%20deals%20Exxon%20has%20made%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-releases%2F2023%2F0601_lcs-nucor-agreement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20plan%20to%20capture%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20store%20carbon%20emissions%20from%20a%20steelmaking%20plant%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Louisiana%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20state%20of%20CCUS%20today%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECCUS%20is%20still%20a%20nascent%20industry%20with%20a%20troubled%20track%20record%2C%20but%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20momentum%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2040%20commercial%20sites%20are%20operating%20around%20the%20world%2C%20with%20another%2050%20capture%20facilities%20expected%20to%20come%20online%20by%202030%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Fenergy-system%2Fcarbon-capture-utilisation-and-storage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20IEA%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Exxon%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.exxonmobil.com%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fdelivering-industrial-solutions%2Fcarbon-capture-and-storage%2Fccs-in-action%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehas%20carbon-capture%20and%20storage%20facilities%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20and%20at%20least%2010%20more%20have%20been%20announced%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20carbon%20capture%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20companies%20certainly%20think%20so%2C%20though%20the%20technology%20is%20still%20a%20major%20flashpoint.%20Many%20climate%20advocates%20argue%20that%20CCUS%20is%20too%20expensive%20to%20develop%20and%20the%20money%20is%20better%20spent%20on%20technology%20already%20proven%20to%20slash%20emissions%20at%20scale%3A%20solar%20panels%2C%20wind%20turbines%2C%20and%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarbon-emissions-2022-record-renewables-growth-solar-wind-iea-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erenewable%20energy%20transition%20is%20sp