r%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F03%2Fbusiness%2Fcar-repairs-electric-vehicles.html%5C%22%3Ereport%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Apfelstadt%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20while%20he'd%20expected%20the%20repair%20wouldn't%20be%20cheap%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20which%20occurred%20February%20in%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio%2C%20was%20at%20first%20believed%20to%20be%20somewhat%20minor%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Times%20report%2C%20which%20said%20the%20other%20driver's%20insurance%20offered%20to%20pay%20about%20%241%2C600.%20But%2C%20after%20the%20electric%20car%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20repair%20shop%20that%20was%20certified%20to%20work%20with%20Rivian%20products%20the%20cost%20jumped%20to%20%2442%2C000%2C%20the%20publication%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20repair%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caranddriver.com%2Frivian%2Fr1t%5C%22%3Eover%20half%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20starting%20price%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20One%20of%20the%20primary%20reasons%20for%20the%20high%20price%20was%20that%20the%20accident%20affected%20a%20panel%20that%20reaches%20from%20the%20back%20of%20the%20vehicle%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20front%20roof%20pillars%20of%20the%20truck%20and%20fixing%20the%20panel%20required%20service%20workers%20to%20remove%20the%20ceiling%20and%20front%20windshield%2C%20the%20Times%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20publication%20also%20attributed%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20repair%20shops%20for%20the%20Rivian%20R1T%20and%20the%20expense%20of%20fixing%20EVs%20that%20rely%20on%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-infotainment-system-best-in-world-beats-bmw-consumer-reports-2019-5%5C%22%3Ehigh-tech%20parts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Like%20Tesla%2C%20Rivian%20does%20not%20use%20dealers.%20The%20company%20has%20certified%20about%20200%20repair%20shops%20in%20North%20Am