t%20Test%20against%20West%20Indies%2C%20having%20scored%20his%20maiden%20Test%20ton%20on%20the%20second%20day%20in%20Dominica.%20Resuming%20the%20innings%20on%20the%20third%20day%20at%20143%2C%20Jaiswal%20needed%20just%207%20runs%20to%20make%20history.%20He%20wasted%20little%20time%20in%20going%20past%20the%20150-run%20mark%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20batter%20to%20do%20that%20on%20his%20debut%20in%20an%20overseas%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20record%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20scoring%20the%20most%20runs%20on%20Test%20debut%20for%20an%20Indian.%20However%2C%20his%20187-run%20knock%20had%20come%20against%20Australia%20at%20home%20(in%20March%202013).%20Even%20Rohit%20Sharma%20scored%20177%20in%20his%20debut%20Test%20innings%20but%20his%20knock%20also%20came%20at%20home%2C%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%202013.%20Sharma%20got%20out%20on%20171%2C%20thus%20becoming%20the%20third%20highest%20scorer%20for%20India%20on%20a%20Test%20debut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20seen%20him%20grow%20from%20close%20quarters%2C%20Jwala%20Singh%20always%20had%20this%20deep-down%20conviction%20that%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20will%20make%20a%20good%20start%20in%20national%20colours%20and%20the%20former%20coach%20is%20glad%20that%20his%20ward%20is%20proving%20him%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20on%20Thursday%20became%20the%2017th%20Indian%20player%20to%20score%20a%20century%20on%20debut%20in%20Test%20cricket%20after%20he%20reached%20the%20three-figure%20mark%20on%20day%20two%20of%20the%20ongoing%20first%20Test%20against%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20reached%20an%20unbeaten%20143%20from%20350%20balls%20on%20the%20second%20day%2C%20giving%20India%20a%20healthy%20lead%20of%20162%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20after%20the%20West%20Indies%20was%20bowled%20out%20for%20a%20mere%20150%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20in%20Dominica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20to%20see%20him%20grow.%20I%20had%20some%20feeling%20that%20he%20would%20start%20well.%20He%20has%20spent%20four%20good%20seasons%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20also%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%20He%20has%20played%20most%20of%20the%20world-class%20bowlers%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jwala%2C%20who%20was%20in%20transit%20in%20the%20UK%20when%20Jaiswal%20brought%20up%20his%20century%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20the%20idea%20about%20playing%20with%20top%20quality%20bowlers.%20As%20a%20player%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20the%20habit%20of%20making%20runs.%20As%20a%20coach%20I%20always%20teach%20my%20players%20to%20see%20the%20ball%20and%20not%20the%20bowler%2C%20and%20try%20to%20react%20to%20the%20ball%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20always%20be%20nine%20fielders%2C%20whatever%20match%20you%20play%2C%20whether%20it's%20T20%20or%20one-day%20or%20Test.%20As%20a%20batter%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20present%20and%20face%20each%20and%20every%20ball%20on%20merit%20and%20believe%20in%20your%20ability.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20Yashasvi%20is%20able%20to%20do%20this%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20is%20proving%20me%20right.%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20had%20moved%20to%20Dadar%20in%20Mumbai%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%20to%20receive%20cricket%20training%20at%20Azad%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Jaiswal%20became%20the%20fourth%20batter%20on%20the%20trot%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20make%20a%20debut%20Test%20century%20for%20India%2C%20joining%20the%20likes%20of%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(vs%20New%20Zealand%2C%202021)%2C%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20(vs%20West%20Indies%2C%202018)%20and%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(vs%20West%20Indies%2C%202013).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A168934