partments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Bansode%20will%20now%20manage%20Sports%20and%20Youth%20Welfare%2C%20and%20Port%20portfolios.%20Aditi%20Takkare%20will%20now%20head%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Welfare%20Department.%20Radhakrishna%20Vikhe-Patil%20has%20been%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Revenue%2C%20Animal%20Husbandry%2C%20and%20Dairy%20Development%20departments.%20Sudhir%20Sachhidanand%20Mungantiwar%20will%20handle%20Forests%2C%20Cultural%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Fisheries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20latest%20reshuffle%2C%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20will%20be%20left%20with%20General%20Administration%2C%20Urban%20Development%2C%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20Transport%2C%20Social%20Justice%2C%20Environment%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Mining%2C%20and%20other%20departments%20which%20have%20not%20been%20assigned%20to%20other%20ministers.%20Meanwhile%2C%20another%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20will%20handle%20Home%2C%20Law%20and%20Justice%2C%20Water%20Resources%20and%20River%20Development%2C%20Energy%2C%20and%20Parliamentary%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20the%20induction%20of%20NCP%20MLAs%20into%20the%20Cabinet%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20the%20legislators%20of%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20who%20feel%20that%20they%20have%20received%20a%20raw%20deal%20with%20the%20latest%20Cabinet%20rejig.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20288%20Assembly%20seats%2C%20a%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20can%20have%20a%20total%20of%2043%20ministries%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20induction%20of%20NCP%20MLAs%20into%20the%20government%2C%20a%20total%20of%2029%20berths%20have%20been%20filled%2C%20and%2014%20are%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20nine%20berths%20going%20to%20the%20NCP%2C%20there%20is%20a%20feeling%20of%20betrayal%20among%20the%20MLA%20of%20older%20allies%2C%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%2