a%20member%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Achille%20Forler%2C%20the%2073-year-old%20founder%20director%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20he%20was%20in%20politics%2C%20though%20he%20gave%20his%20address%20as%20Hedgevar%20Bhavan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20signature%20on%20his%20membership%20card%20is%20that%20of%20my%20wife%20Chantal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185530%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22831%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185530%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-1.jpg%20831w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185530%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-1-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663223%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReceipt%20showing%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20membership%20at%20Alliance%20Francaise%20(AF)%20Ahmedabad.%20Photo%3A%20Vibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForler%20and%20Modi%20are%20contemporaries%20and%20became%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20over%201%2C000%20members%2C%20but%20Narendrabhai%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20I%20made%20a%20connection%20with.%20I%20would%20be%20standing%20at%20the%20door%20greeting%20people%20at%20every%20cultural%20event%20and%20I%20remember%20Narendrabhai%20was%20a%20regular.%20One%20time%20he%20came%20to%20my%20office%20asking%20permission%20to%20borrow%20an%20expensive%20coffee%20table%20book%20on%20photography%20from%20the%20library.%20I%20remembered%20that%20and%20later%2C%20when%20the%20famous%20French%20photographer%20Henri%20Cartier-Bresson%20was%20visiting%20Ahmedabad%2C%20I%20invited%20Narendrabhai%20to%20meet%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Forler%2C%20who%20moved%20on%20to%20the%20French%20Embassy%20in%20Delhi%20in%201989%20and%20now%20lives%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22831%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India.jpg%20831w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14185759%2FVibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-Vibes-Of-India-300x219.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663225%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReceipt%20showing%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20membership%20at%20Alliance%20Francaise%20(AF)%20Ahmedabad.%20Photo%3A%20Vibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20remained%20a%20member%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20for%20eight%20years%20and%20judging%20by%20his%20speech%20in%20Paris%2C%20he%20has%20happy%20memories.%20Pavan%20Bakeri%2C%20President%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%2C%20first%20heard%20of%20the%20connection%20in%202013%2C%20when%20Modi%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20to%20invite%20him%20to%20a%20concert%20we%20were%20organising%20and%20he%20told%20me%20he%20was%20once%20a%20regular%20member%20of%20AF.%20He%20said%20he%20used%20to%20use%20the%20library%20a%20lot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Modi%20never%20did%20attend%20that%20concert%20and%20AF%20Ahmedabad%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20never%20leveraged%20the%20connection%20(though%20it%20did%20dig%20out%20the%20original%20membership%20card%20and%20receipt%20and%20send%20him%20a%20copy%20when%20he%20became%20PM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVO!%20spoke%20to%20Emmanuel%20Bottiau%2C%20Director%20of%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20as%20he%20was%20waiting%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Paris%20from%20Delhi%20airport.%20We%20asked%20him%3A%20how%20did%20it%20feel%20to%20hear%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Thursday%3F%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20happy%2C%20of%20course.%20We%20were%20aware%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20a%20member%2C%20but%20we%20never%20publicised%20it.%20AF%20is%20a%20cultural%20association%20and%20we%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20get%20into%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20some%20of%20the%20most%20eminent%20names%20in%20Ahmedabad%20society%2C%20AF%20Ahmedabad%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20international%20cultural%20centres%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20it%20must%20have%20been%20an%20aspirational%20draw%20for%20the%2031-year-old%20Modi.%20The%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20first%20president%20was%20Mrinalini%20Sarabhai%2C%20who%20was%20succeeded%20by%20B.V.%20Doshi.%20One%20of%20the%20later%20presidents%20was%20photographer%20Parmanand%20Dalwadi%2C%20who%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20member%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20recall%20meeting%20Mr.%20Modi%20there.%20He%20was%20not%20a%20well-known%20person%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20in%20the%20early%2080s%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20anyone%20would%20have%20recognised%20the%20young%20Modi%20as%20a%20future%20prime%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20days%2C%20he%20kept%20to%20himself.%20He%20was%20very%20discreet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Achille%20Forler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20original%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fno-narendra-modi-was-not-the-first-member-of-alliance-francaise-ahmedabad-but-he-was-close%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689342395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14190359%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-14T190344.694.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fno-narendra-modi-wasnt-the-first-member-of-alliance-francaise-ahmedabad-but-he-was-close%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20the%20member%20of%20the%20French%20cultural%20centre%20in%20Ahmedabad%20in%201981%20and%20remained%20so%20for%20eight%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fno-narendra-modi-wasnt-the-first-member-of-alliance-francaise-ahmedabad-but-he-was-close%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20How%20Does%20India%E2%80%99s%20First%20AI-Based%20Driverless%20Car%20Work%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20driverless%20car%20carrying%20passengers%20cruising%20on%20roads.%20It%20sounds%20like%20something%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304074%2Fbook-recommendations-by-ira-mukhoty-on-history-science-wolf-hall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20a%20sci-fi%20novel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20company%20Minus%20Zero%20has%20made%20it%20possible!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%2C%20Gagandeep%20Reehal%20and%20Gursimran%20Kalra%2C%20were%20in%20college%20when%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20something%20as%20futuristic%20as%20a%20driverless%20car%20came%20to%20them.%20With%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20duo%20started%20Minus%20Zero%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI%20mobility%20company%20and%20built%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20self-driving%20car%20called%20%E2%80%98zPod%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWondering%20how%20the%20car%20works%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20network%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124905%2Fartificial-intelligence-cctv-cameras-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-resolution%20cameras%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20are%20strategically%20placed%20on%20the%20car.%20These%20cameras%20capture%20real-time%20images%20of%20their%20surroundings%20and%20transmit%20them%20to%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291211%2Fiit-palakkad-offers-free-course-on-artificial-intelligence-ai-how-to-apply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20AI%20System%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20system%20makes%20decisions%20based%20on%20these%20images%20and%20drives%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20ecosystem%20for%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20So%20when%20we%20took%20on%20the%20task%20of%20building%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%2C%20we%20also%20took%20up%20the%20task%20of%20building%20up%20an%20ecosystem%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gursimran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20car%20is%20also%20a%20step%20towards%20safer%20roads%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20risks%20of%20human%20errors%20while%20driving.%20zPod%20can%20drive%20on%20any%20kind%20of%20environmental%20or%20geographical%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20was%20confident%20about%20their%20design%2C%20others%20were%20unsure%20if%20India%20was%20the%20right%20place%20to%20launch%20the%20vehicle.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20people%20who%20questioned%20us%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20move%20our%20innovation%20to%20a%