ey%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20for%20allegedly%20receiving%20and%20possessing%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20received%20in%20the%20scam%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20respondents%20(ED)%20can%20take%20custody%20for%20further%20investigation%20cannot%20be%20denied.%20The%20respondent%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20had%20a%20right%20to%20get%20custody.%20I%20would%20align%20my%20opinion%20with%20the%20reason%20given%20by%20Justice%20Bharatha%20Chakravarthy%20in%20this%20aspect%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Karthikeyan%20ruled%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fmadras-high-court-senthil-balaji-ed-police-custody-232750%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Livelaw.in%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20the%20third%20judge%20assigned%20to%20hear%20the%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20(HCP)%20filed%20by%20Balaji%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Megala%2C%20who%20prayed%20for%20declaring%20the%20arrest%20illegal%20and%20setting%20him%20at%20liberty%2C%20following%20a%20split%20verdict%20by%20a%20two-judge%20division%20bench%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Nisha%20Banu%20and%20Justice%20Chakravarthy%20of%20the%20high%20court%20had%20issued%20differing%20rulings.%20Justice%20Banu%20held%20the%20arrest%20illegal%20and%20ordered%20the%20immediate%20release%20of%20the%20minister%20while%20noting%20that%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20lacked%20the%20power%20to%20take%20custody%20for%20interrogation.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Justice%20Chakravarthy%20ruled%20that%20there%20was%20no%20illegality%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20Balaji%2C%20noting%20that%20ED%20is%20well%20within%20its%20rights%20to%20take%20Balaji%20under%20custody%20for%20interrogation.%20He%20dismissed%20the%20habeas%20corpus%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20split%20verdict%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20assigned%20to%20Karthikeyan%2C%20the%20third%20judge%20in%20the%20case.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fmadras-high-court-tie-breaker-judge-rules-against-release-senthil-balaji%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20investigation%20requires%20custody%20then%20custody%20is%20to%20be%20given%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20right%20%E2%80%A6%20But%20no%20accused%20has%20a%20right%20to%20frustrate%20inquiry.%20Even%20prior%20to%20his%20ill%20health%2C%20the%20accused%20refused%20to%20accept%20grounds%20of%20arrest%20and%20then%20claimed%20he%20was%20not%20provided%20grounds%20of%20arrest.%20This%20cannot%20be%20considered%20by%20this%20Court.%20It%20must%20be%20declared%20a%20falsity%20%E2%80%A6%20When%20arrest%20is%20possible%2C%20then%20seeking%20custody%20is%20also%20permissible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Karthikeyan%20directed%20the%20court%20registry%20to%20forward%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20high%20court%20for%20a%20final%20order%20to%20be%20passed%20considering%20his%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20passing%20his%20verdict%2C%20Justice%20Karthikeyan%20considered%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%20%3Cem%3EY%20Balaji%20v.%20Karthik%20Desai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20wherein%20the%20top%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20discharge%20Balaji%20in%20the%20cash-for-jobs%20scam%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20are%20very%20telling.%20They%20go%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20matter%20to%20show%20why%20the%20June%2013%20search%20was%20conducted%20by%20ED.%20This%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20was%20not%20pointed%20out%20before%20the%20division%20bench%20by%20either%20side.%20I%20will%20be%20failing%20in%20my%20duty%20if%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20examine%20this%20judgment%20as%20that%20is%20what%20led%20to%20the%20ED%20proceedings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Karthikeyan%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fmadras-high-court-tie-breaker-judge-rules-against-release-senthil-balaji%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20Balaji%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20government%20of%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20had%20an%20angiogram%20hours%20after%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20early%20June%20in%20connection%20with%20money%20laundering%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Karthikeyan%20took%20into%20consideration%20Balaji%E2%80%99s%20plea%20that%20his%20arrest%20by%20ED%20and%20detention%20had%20affected%20his%20well-being.%20Balaji%20also%20said%2C%20in%20his%20petition%2C%20that%20he%20was%20not%20intimated%20of%20the%20grounds%20on%20which%20he%20was%20being%20arrested%2C%20thereby%20violating%20his%20constitutional%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20ED%2C%20it%20said%20Balaji%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20the%20probe%20agency%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthrew%20tantrums%2C%20threatened%20officials%2C%20and%20also%C2%A0refused%20to%20sign%20the%20memo%20of%20grounds%20of%20arrest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20respondents%20were%20at%20his%20(Balaji%E2%80%99s)%20doors%20since%20June%2013.%20He%20should%20have%20known%20why.%20He%20can%E2%80%99t%20claim%20innocence%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20the%20reasons%20to%20grant%20remand%20outweigh%20the%20objections%20to%20remand%2C%20then%20certainly%20such%20remand%20will%20have%20to%20be%20granted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Karthikeyan%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalaji%20is%20still%20continuing%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Cabinet%2C%20however%20without%20any%20portfolio.%20He%20is%20currently%20under%20post-operative%20care%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20with%20regard%20to%20Senthil%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20resorting%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpolitics%20of%20intimidation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publish