.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcitigroup-profit-drops-36-as-trading-slump-casts-cloud-over-earnings-123071400734_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%3A%20Lesbian%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20Harrowing%20Journey%20Shines%20Light%20on%20Continuing%20Dangers%20of%20%E2%80%98Conversion%20Therapy%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14153359%2Fdustin-humes-BAo2jd67Jhs-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErnakulam%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20dangers%20and%20immorality%20of%20using%20%E2%80%98conversion%20therapy%E2%80%99%20on%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20highlighted%20across%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20were%20brought%20forth%20in%20Kerala%20recently%2C%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20lesbian%20couple%20Afeefa%20and%20Sumayya%20Sherin.%20The%20case%20also%20points%20to%20blind%20spots%20in%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20threats%20queer%20people%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20phone%20July%205%2C%20Afeefa%20described%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20forced%20conversion%20therapy%20her%20family%20made%20her%20undergo%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Kozhikode.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20unable%20to%20feel%20my%20legs%20while%20walking.%20I%20was%20forcefully%20medicated%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2021%20year%20old%20said.%20She%20paused%20multiple%20times%20as%20she%20spoke.%20In%20the%20hospital%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20was%20forcefully%20injected%20with%20medication%20after%20she%20refused%20to%20take%20them%20orally.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20appetite%20and%20sleeping%20patterns%20have%20been%20affected%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20long%20as%20I%20was%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20as%20days%20went%20on%20from%2010%20to%2015%2C%20the%20dosage%20increased.%20Sumayya%20had%20already%20told%20the%20media%20that%20I%20will%20be%20subjected%20to%20conversion%20therapy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Afeefa%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Afeefa%20and%20Sumayya%20are%20together%20again%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20road%20here%20has%20been%20hard%2C%20and%20they%20still%20feel%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20violence%20Afeefa%20was%20subjected%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20Afeefa%20and%20Sumayya%20decided%20to%20come%20out%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Vanaja%2C%20a%20community-based%20organisation.%20The%20collective%20works%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20gender%20minorities%20and%20other%20oppressed%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2027%2C%20the%20two%20started%20living%20together%20in%20Ernakulam.%20Their%20families%20filed%20missing%20persons%E2%80%99%20reports%2C%20but%20the%20couple%20was%20granted%20protection%20by%20the%20Malappuram%20judicial%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20four%20months%20after%20they%20moved%20in%20together%2C%20on%20May%2030%2C%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20family%20arrived%20and%20took%20her%20away.%20Not%20knowing%20where%20to%20go%20or%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20worried%20that%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20family%20may%20force%20her%20into%20conversion%20therapy%2C%20Sumayya%20decided%20to%20file%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehabeas%20corpus%3C%2Fem%3E%20petition%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sumayya%20and%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20case%20and%20other%20cases%20they%20have%20worked%20on%2C%20queer%20activist%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Vanaja%20Collective%20M.%20Sulfath%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vanaja%20collective%20has%20followed%20the%20existing%20rules%20of%20law%20to%20gain%20justice.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20at%20the%20police%20station%20or%20the%20government-run%20one%20stop%20centre%2C%20a%20negative%20approach%20to%20these%20young%20women%20was%20evident.%20They%20behave%20in%20a%20way%20that%20enhances%20all%20the%20violence%20we%20endure.%20We%20were%20forced%20to%20file%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20only%20because%20of%20the%20inaction%20and%20patronising%20approach%20by%20the%20police.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Transgender%20Applicants%20to%20Police%20Forces%20Encounter%20Many%20Obstacles%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-transgender-people-obstacles-police-forces%5C%22%3ETransgender%20Applicants%20to%20Police%20Forces%20Encounter%20Many%20Obstacles%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20approach%20the%20police%20with%20the%20petitioner%2C%20seeking%20action%2C%20they%20tell%20us%20the%20woman%20is%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20so%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20that%3F%20This%20inaction%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20file%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%2C%20mostly%20not%20affordable%20for%20us.%20The%20existing%20laws%20are%20not%20protective%2C%20that%20is%20one%20big%20challenge%20while%20handling%20cases%20like%20this.%20In%20the%20Sumayya-Afeefa%20case%2C%20they%20had%20already%20gained%20a%20court%20order%20and%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20family%20happened%20at%20an%20unexpected%20moment.%20Even%20then%2C%20it%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20retired%20police%20officials%20and%20social%20activists%20were%20involved%20in%20separating%20these%20two%20women.%20The%20law%20enforcing%20system%20and%20the%20family%20opposes%20the%20couple%2C%20so%20an%20immense%20challenge%20is%20created%20during%20crisis%20management.%20Their%20lives%20after%20rescue%20too%20remain%20a%20question%2C%20will%20they%20be%20attacked%20again%3F%20If%20they%20are%20detained%20again%2C%20who%20will%20be%20there%20to%20support%20them%3F%20I%20think%20the%20proper%20enforcement%20of%20existing%20laws%20itself%20will%20eliminate%20these%20challenges.%20The%20main%20problem%20is%20that%20they%20%5Bthe%20police%5D%20are%20bound%20by%20morality%20and%20beliefs%20which%20restrain%20them%20from%20enforcing%20the%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sulfath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourt%20proceedings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Sumayya%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%2C%20the%20court%20agreed%20to%20senior%20advocate%20Babu%20Karukappadath%E2%80%99s%20request%20that%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20family%20be%20given%2010%20days%20to%20present%20her%20before%20the%20court.%20This%20was%20a%20questionable%20decision%2C%20given%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20granted%20protection%20by%20the%20judicial%20magistrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Afeefa%20was%20presented%20before%20the%20court%2C%20she%20reportedly%20told%20the%20judges%20that%20while%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Sumayya%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20go%20home%20with%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20detenu%20was%20presented%20in%20the%20open%20court%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20the%20judge%20said%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20heard%20in%20the%20chamber.%20It%20is%20written%20in%20the%20order%20that%20the%20detenu%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Sumayya%20and%20now%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20with%20the%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Fourth%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20court%20reporter%20Shabna%20Ziyad%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20Justice%20P.B.%20Suresh%20Kumar%20and%20Justice%20Shobhana%20Annamma%20Eapan%20closed%20the%20petition%20on%20June%2019%20and%20said%20Afeefa%20would%20go%20back%20with%20her%20parents%2C%20as%20she%20herself%20had%20asked.%20In%20the%20local%20media%2C%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20statements%20were%20widely%20misreported%20%E2%80%93%20with%20claims%20that%20she%20had%20said%20she%20no%20longer%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Sumayya.%20Soon%20after%20the%20court%20closed%20the%20petition%2C%20Sumayya%20received%20an%20SOS%20message%20from%20Afeefa%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20moment%20when%20she%20was%20brought%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Afeefa%20is%20sad%20that%20the%20court%20did%20not%20take%20into%20account%20what%20kind%20of%20pressures%20and%20medication%20she%20may%20have%20been%20under%20while%20making%20her%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20vulnerability%20should%E2%80%99ve%20been%20considered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20court%20hearing%2C%20Afeefa%20managed%20to%20inform%20Sumayya%20through%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20phone%20that%20she%20had%20been%20forced%20into%20conversion%20therapy%20at%20Manohar%20Hospital%2C%20Kozhikode.%20Afeefa%20informed%20Sumayya%20that%20one%20Dr%20Mohan%20Sundaram%20told%20her%20that%20homosexuality%20is%20%E2%80%98against%20nature%E2%80%99%20when%20she%20insisted%20that%20she%20wants%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Sumayya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%20gave%20me%20a%20book%20on%20psychiatry%20to%20read.%20The%20book%20said%20homosexuality%20is%20a%20disorder.%20Even%20after%20reading%20the%20book%20I%20kept%20on%20telling%20the%20doctor%20and%20the%20counsellors%20at%20the%20Manohar%20Hospital%20that%20this%20is%20what%20I%20am%20and%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Afeefa%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2027%2C%20based%20on%20information%20from%20Sumayya%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20protection%20officers%20went%20to%20rescue%20Afeefa%2C%20and%20reported%20that%20her%20family%20had%20been%20using%20force%20against%20her.%20The%20officers%20were%20surrounded%20by%20a%20crowd%20of%20men%20gathered%20near%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20filed%20a%20case%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20said%20that%20since%20the%20court%20had%20closed%20the%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%2C%20they%20require%20an%20order%20from%20the%20district%20collector%20to%20act%20on%20the%20issue.%20In%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20the%20family%20had%20to%20withdraw%20from%20this%20tussle%20as%20the%20police%20too%20got%20involved.%20Sumayya%20and%20Afeefa%20later%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20a%20mediator%20had%20come%20in%20between%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20keep%20silent%20about%20the%20violence%2C%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20live%20together%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dangers%20of%20%E2%80%98conversion%20therapy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%20Nasrin%2C%20a%20queer%20rights%20activist%20and%20political%20analyst%2C%20condemned%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20allow%20Afeefa%E2%80%99s%20family%2010%20days%20before%20presenting%20her%20in%20court.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20like%20the%20judicial%20process%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20danger%20of%20conversion%20therapy%2C%20which%20must%20be%20understood%20as%20a%20serious%20one.%20Mostly%20the%20violence%20on%20queer%20individuals%20would%20be%20meted%20out%20by%20the%20biological%20family.%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20court%20assuming%20that%20the%20woman%20will%20be%20safer%20with%20her%20parents.%20I%20felt%20the%20court%20ignored%20the%20possibility%20of%20conversion%20therapy%20in%20this%20case.%20Also%2C%20I%20wonder%20how%20a%20magistrate%20court%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20left%20unseen%20by%20the%20high%20court.%20To%20approve%20their%20rights%2C%20the%20court%20just%20had%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20both%20are%20adults%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nasrin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shreya%20Mariam%20Salim%20of%20Thiruvananthapuram%20medical%20college%20conducted%20a%20survey%20among%20queer%20individuals%20to%20learn%20the%20persistence%20of%20conversion%20therapy%20for%20her%20PG%20course%20in%20psychiatry.%20During%20the%20survey%20conducted%20in%202021-2022%2C%20130%20participants%20responded.%20Forty-five%20percent%20of%20the%20queer%20individuals%20who%20responded%20to%20the%20survey%20said%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20conversion%20therapy.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F36745044%2F%5C%22%3Epaper%20published%20on%20their%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Homosexuality%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20authored%20by%20Salim%2C%20Dr%20Lalchand%20Anilal%20and%20Dr%20Anil%20Prabhakaran%20talked%20about%20the%20challenges%20facing%20the%20social%20and%20physical%20health%20of%20queer%20individuals.%20The%20paper%20looks%20into%20the%20means%20through%20which%20%E2%80%98conversion%20therapy%E2%80%99%20is%20carried%20out%20and%20its%20impacts.%20It%20acknowledged%20international%20studies%20that%20points%20out%20that%20the%20conversion%20therapy%20attempts%20made%20by%20parents%20trouble%20an%20individual%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20suicidal%20tendency%2C%20hurt%20dignity%2C%20drug%20usage%2C%20lowered%20self%20esteem%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Love%20in%20a%20Time%20of%20Intolerance%3A%C2%A0How%20Policy%20and%20Social%20Prejudice%20Are%20Holding%20Back%20the%20Romantic%20Indian%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Flove-jihad-prejudice-marriage-act%5C%22%3ELove%20in%20a%20Time%20of%20Intolerance%3A%C2%A0How%20Policy%20and%20Social%20Prejudice%20Are%20Holding%20Back%20the%20Romantic%20Indian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20psychotherapy%20was%20the%20commonest%20method%20used%20for%20sexual%20orientation%20change%20(28.8%25).%20As%20many%20as%2047.5%25%20of%20them%20self-prompted%20such%20attempts%2C%20while%2037.3%25%20were%20subjected%20to%20such%20attempts%20by%20their%20families.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20may%20be%20even%20more%20relevant%20in%20the%20Indian%20setting%2C%20where%20individual%20autonomy%20is%20often%20sacrificed%20to%20maintain%20family%20integrity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20paper%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversion%20therapy%20is%20widely%20practiced%20in%20south%20India.%20In%20May%202020%2C%20Anjana%20Hareesh%2C%20a%20student%20from%20Taliparamba%2C%20Kannur%20who%20identified%20as%20bisexual%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fkerala-student-dies-goa-death-puts-focus-inhuman-conversion-therapy-queer-people-124683%5C%22%3Edied%20by%20suicide%20after%20going%20through%20a%20harrowing%20episode%20of%20conversion%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hareesh%20was%20subjected%20to%20conversion%20therapy%20by%20one%20Dr%20N.S.%20Moni%2C%20a%20Coimbatore-based%20psychologist.%20She%20was%20taken%20to%20Coimbatore%20by%20a%20regional%20organisation%20named%20Hindu%20Democratic%20Front.%20She%20was%20also%20taken%20to%20Karunasai%2C%20a%20psychiatric%20hospital%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20and%20Shalom%2C%20a%20deaddiction%20plus%20mental%20health%20centre%20in%20Palakad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Moni%20considered%20homosexuality%20to%20be%20like%20addiction%2C%20a%20survivor%20of%20Moni%E2%80%99s%20conversion%20therapy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkeyboardjournal.com%2Fthe-role-of-hindu-democratic-front-and-south-indias-illegal-psychological-practices-in-anjana-harishs-suicide%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%20in%202020%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Moni%E2%80%99s%20consultation%20fee%20ranged%20from%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkeyboardjournal.com%2Fthe-role-of-hindu-democratic-front-and-south-indias-illegal-psychological-practices-in-anjana-harishs-suicide%2F%5C%22%3EPrevious%20reporting%20has%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Dr%20Srinivas%20who%20works%20at%20the%20Kovai%20medical%20center%20hospital%20too%20does%20conversion%20therapy.%20Srinivas%20tells%20parents%20that%20homosexuality%20can%20be%20treated%20and%20cured.%20Dr%20N.%20Dinesh%20in%20Amrita%20hospital%20Kochi%20too%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20forced%20medication%20by%20several%20queer%20individuals%20and%20persons%20in%20interfaith%20and%20intercaste%20relationships.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20has%20excluded%20homosexuality%20from%20the%20list%20of%20mental%20illnesses%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20medical%20field%20still%20treats%20it%20as%20a%20mental%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20there%20are%20only%20very%20few%20studies%20that%20have%20been%20conducted%20on%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salim%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20this%20is%20the%20first%20study%20on%20conversion%20therapy%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20carried%20out%20in%20India.%20We%20studied%20the%20impacts%20of%20conversion%20therapy%20on%20individuals%20and%20what%20are%20the%20mental%20health%20implications.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20relied%20on%20data%20on%20conversion%20therapy%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20on%20data%20from%20direct%20qualitative%20studies.%20Reasons%20that%20lead%20to%20conversion%20therapy%20are%20mostly%20pressure%20from%20families%2C%20religion%2C%20stigma%2C%20pressure%20to%20continue%20in%20a%20marital%20relationship%2C%20etc.%20Conversion%20therapy%20is%20illegal%2C%20considering%20the%20rights%20of%20a%20patient%20in%20the%20Indian%20Mental%20Health%20Care%20Act.%20I%20think%20more%20cases%20of%20conversion%20therapy%20are%20being%20reported%20now.%20We%20need%20to%20thoroughly%20follow%20up%20on%20such%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salim%20said.%20Based%20on%20community-based%20organisation%20Queerala%E2%80%99s%20petition%2C%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20had%20given%20instructions%20to%20the%20government%20to%20implement%20action%20against%20those%20promoting%20conversion%20therapies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Padma%20Lakshmi%2C%20a%20trans%20woman%20practicing%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%2C%20thinks%20that%20conversion%20therapy%20should%20be%20penalised.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20psychiatric%20associations%20that%20oppose%20conversion%20therapy%2C%20but%20no%20law%20that%20penalises%20conversion%20therapy.%20Conversion%20therapy%20should%20be%20penalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Padma%20Lakshmi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20A.%20Rajasimhan%2C%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%2C%20agrees%3A%20%E2%80%9CConversion%20therapy%20is%20an%20illegal%20practice.%20Practitioners%20are%20punishable%20under%20IPC%20326%2C%20the%20hospital%20must%20be%20shut%20down%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20queer%20people%E2%80%99s%20agency%20and%20choice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20writ%20petition%2C%20Sumayya%20had%20pointed%20to%20a%20Kerala%20high%20court%20judgment%20from%20September%2024%2C%202018.%20It%20was%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20woman%20named%20Shreeja%20for%20her%20partner%2C%20who%20had%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20her%20family%20even%20when%20there%20was%20a%20magistrate%E2%80%99s%20court%20order%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20live%20together.%20Shreeja%E2%80%99s%20partner%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20government%20mental%20hospital%20in%20Peroorkada.%20The%20complainant%20could%20meet%20her%20partner%20in%20the%20hospital.%20The%20court%20realised%20the%20partner%20of%20the%20petitioner%20is%20being%20held%20against%20her%20will.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justice%20C.K.%20Abdul%20Rehim%20and%20Justice%20R.%20Narayana%20Pisharadi%20released%20a%20judgment%20underlining%20the%20free%20will%20of%20the%20detenu.%20There%20exist%20several%20other%20such%20cases%20where%20judges%20have%20noted%20that%20law%20enforcement%20cannot%20ignore%20queer%20people%E2%80%99s%20agency%20and%20free%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20Mekhal%2C%20a%20queer%20rights%20activist%20who%20works%20with%20community-based%20organisation%20Sahayatrika%2C%20says%20that%20law%20enforcement%20groups%20are%20still%20not%20free%20from%20the%20judgments%20based%20on%20social%20morality.%20With%20years%20of%20field%20experience%20of%20working%20to%20rescue%20queer%20individuals%20in%20parental%20custody%2C%20Mekhal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSocial%20morality%20of%20those%20who%20function%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%20influence%20these%20cases.%20Even%20when%20the%20laws%20are%20protective%2C%20the%20judges%20have%20harassed%20us%20and%20spoken%20against%20the%20law.%20In%20the%20police%20station%20too%2C%20because%20of%20this%20perceived%20morality%2C%20they%20act%20so%20adamant.%20Even%20when%20they%20know%20it%20is%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20internalise%20certain%20things.%20There%20is%20a%20specific%20group%20of%20people%20who%20oppose%20the%20rights%20of%20queer%20individuals%20outright%20and%20such%20groups%20get%20support.%20%E2%80%A6The%20police%20can%20convince%20the%20family%20to%20see%20what%20is%20right.%20But%20mostly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20police%20who%20takes%20the%20initiative%20to%20send%20the%20person%20back%20with%20the%20family.%20Not%20much%20has%20changed%20here.%20It%20is%20after%20these%20judgments%20%5Bmentioned%20above%5D%20that%20some%20young%20police%20officers%20started%20understanding%20things.%20In%20the%20past%20three%20or%20four%20years%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20go%20to%20the%20police%20stations%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20police%20more%20easily%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20long%20struggle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMrudula%20Bhavani%20is%20a%20journalist%20based%20in%20Ernakulam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689337824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14153359%2Fdustin-humes-BAo2jd67Jhs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Fkerala-lesbian-couples-harrowing-journey-shines-light-on-continuing-dangers-of-conversion-therapy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kerala%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20response%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20Afeefa%20and%20Sumayya%20Sherin%20points%20to%20blind%20spots%20in%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20threats%20queer%20people%20face%20and%20law%20enforcement%E2%80%99s%20skewed%20perspective%20on%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https