20trade%20deficit%20with%20China%20was%20%2469.38%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findia-china-trade-deficit-2022-imports-exports%5C%22%3EDespite%20Frosty%20Relations%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Trade%20With%20China%20Reaches%20Record%20Levels%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20trade%20with%20other%20countries%20has%20also%20decreased.%20Reuters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fasia%2Fchinas-june-exports-fall-124-imports-drop-68-2023-07-13%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20its%20exports%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20is%20the%20top%20destination%20for%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20decreased%20by%2012%25%20between%20January%20and%20June%202023%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20decrease%20out%20of%20all%20its%20major%20trading%20partners.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20global%20downturn%20in%20goods%20demand%20will%20continue%20to%20weigh%20on%20exports%20%E2%80%A6%20But%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20decline%20in%20foreign%20demand%20is%20probably%20already%20behind%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zichun%20Huang%2C%20China%20economist%20at%20Capital%20Economics%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20China%E2%80%99s%20customs%20department%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20General%20Administration%20of%20Customs%20(GAC)%2C%20said%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20export%20situation%20was%20caused%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20weak%20global%20economic%20recovery%2C%20slowing%20global%20trade%20and%20investment%2C%20and%20rising%20unilateralism%2C%20protectionism%20and%20geopolitics%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20China%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20decrease%20in%20exports%20to%20all%