rc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F13105808%2FScreenshot-2023-05-13-at-10.58.03-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMizoram%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20vice-president%2C%20R.%20Vanramchhuanga%2C%20has%20tendered%20his%20resignation%2C%20accusing%20Union%20and%20Manipur%20governments%20of%20supporting%20the%20burning%20down%20of%20churches%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vanramchhuanga%2C%20a%20total%20of%20357%20churches%2C%20pastors%E2%80%99%20quarters%2C%20and%20office%20buildings%20of%20different%20churches%20have%20so%20far%20been%20%E2%80%9Cburned%20into%20ashes%20by%20Meitei%20militants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20protest%20against%20this%20act%20of%20criminal%20injustice%20to%20Christians%20and%20the%20Christian%20religion%2C%20I%20do%20hereby%20submit%20my%20resignation%20as%20the%20state%20vice%20president%2C%20of%20BJP%20Mizoram%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Mizoram%20BJP%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20neither%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20nor%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20said%20a%20word%20condemning%20the%20burning%20down%20of%20churches.%20Not%20a%20word%20of%20condemnation%20has%20come%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20too%20on%20the%20burning%20down%20of%20churches.%20%E2%80%9CTherefore%20I%20do%20believe%20that%20the%20massive%20demolition%20of%20Christian%20Churches%20in%20Manipur%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20state%20and%20Central%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanramchhuanga%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmizoram-bjp-vice-president-resigns-to-protest-attacks-on-churches-in-manipur-8834718%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20incidents%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%9Cgave%20credence%20to%20allegations%20of%20the%20BJP%20being%20an%20%E2%80%98anti-Christian%20party'%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20leaders%2C%20as%20well%20as%20central%20leaders%2C%20should%20have%20expressed%20their%20condemnation%20of%20the%20miscreants%E2%80%99%20acts%2C%20and%20they%20must%20do%20something%20to%20safeguard%20or%20console%20the%20victims%E2%80%A6%20Mizoram%20is%20a%20Christian%20state%20but%20some%20other%20parties%20used%20to%20criticise%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20anti-Christian%20party%2C%20which%20has%20influenced%20particularly%20women%20believers.%20The%20idea%20has%20come%20into%20effect%20in%20Manipur.%20People%20can%20say%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20really%20an%20anti-Christian%20party%E2%80%A6%20As%20an%20ordained%20Church%20elder%2C%20I%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20ideas%20of%20my%20people%2C%20my%20Church%20people.%20As%20a%20Church%20leader%2C%20I%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20his%20decision%20to%20snap%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20clash%20between%20Meities%20and%20Kukis%20in%20Manipur%20also%20has%20a%20religious%20angle%2C%20as%20the%20large%20population%20of%20Meities%20is%20Hindus%2C%20and%20Kukis%20and%20Nagas%20are%20Christians.%20Since%20the%20violence%20broke%20on%20May%203%2C%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20has%20claimed%20over%20200%20lives%2C%20and%20also%20resulted%20in%20desecration%20and%20torching%20of%20a%20number%20of%20churches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dominant%20Mizo%20community%20of%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20shares%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20the%20Kuki-Zumi%20community%20of%20Manipur.%20Manipur%20has%2041.39%25%20Hindus%2C%2041.29%25%20Christians%2C%20and%208.4%25%20Muslims.%20The%20Christian%20community%20makes%20up%20more%20than%2087%25%20of%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%20has%20been%20keeping%20a%20close%20tab%20on%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20has%20even%20sheltered%20over%2012%2C000%20displaced%20Kuki-Zomi%20people%20from%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20political%20leaders%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20including%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20have%20publicly%20expressed%20support%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%20demand%20made%20by%20Kuki-Zomis.%20Even%20Mizoram%20BJP%20leadership%2C%20in%20May%2C%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20stating%20that%20it%20found%20the%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20expand%20its%20footprint%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20it%20had%20won%20an%20Assembly%20seat%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fbjp-wins-village-council-election-in-mizoram-beats-ruling-party-mnf-state-prepares-for-upcoming-polls-mizoramelections-bjp-mnf-101682060138192.html%5C%22%3Eemerged%20victorious%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20village%20council%20election%20for%20Mara%20Autonomous%20District%20Council%20(MADC)%20after%20beating%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20Mizoram%20goes%20to%20Assembly%20polls%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689333082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F13105808%2FScreenshot-2023-05-13-at-10.58.03-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-bjp-vice-president-resigns-says-manipur-union-govts-supported-demolition-of-churches%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'To%20protest%20against%20this%20act%20of%20criminal%20injustice%20to%20Christians%20and%20the%20Christian%20religion%2C%20I%20do%20hereby%20submit%20my%20resignation%20as%20the%20state%20vice%20president%2C%20of%20BJP%20Mizoram%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C'%20said%20R.