0in%20terms%20of%20data%2C%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20imposed%20on%20Manipur%20has%20triggered%20an%20apocalyptic%20calamity.%20The%20violence-ridden%20state%20has%20suffered%20a%20fatal%20blow%20on%20account%20of%20the%20hackneyed%20policy%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20deems%20shutting%20down%20the%20internet%20as%20the%20easiest%20route%20to%20salvage%20Manipur%20from%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20precipice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalf%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Kerala%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20by%20declaring%20the%20internet%20to%20be%20a%20basic%20human%20right%20and%20made%20clear%20its%20intent%20to%20bring%20every%20household%20under%20internet%20coverage.%20As%20a%20sequel%20to%20this%2C%20the%20state%20last%20month%20launched%20an%20ambitious%20public%20centric%20project%20K-FON%20(Kerala%20Fibre%20Optic%20Project)%20for%20providing%20high%20speed%20internet%20for%20free%20for%20poor%20and%20at%20affordable%20rates%20to%20others.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20project%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20landmark%20judgments%20including%20that%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F82461587%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2020)%20declaring%20the%20paramount%20importance%20of%20internet%20in%20different%20spheres%20of%20life%20and%20livelihood.%20Nevertheless%2C%20various%20governments%20have%20been%20going%20around%20imposing%20internet%20shut%20downs%20with%20scant%20respect%20even%20to%20the%20unanimous%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Communications%20and%20Information%20Technology%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20have%20been%20witnessing%20suspension%20of%20internet%20services.%20This%20year%20itself%20there%20have%20been%2C%20so%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Finternet-shutdown-india-loss-financial%5C%22%3Earound%20three%20dozen%20such%20instances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Manipur%20being%20the%20latest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20strife-torn%20Manipur%20revealed%20the%20crippling%20impact%20of%20internet%20shutdown%20as%20it%20has%20struck%20the%20people%20as%20a%20second%20calamity.%20Plains%20and%20hills%20alike%2C%20the%20internet%20vacuum%20has%20been%20bleeding%20the%20entire%20populace.%20It%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20state.%20Economic%20activities%20have%20come%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt.%20Even%20those%20remote%20households%20which%20relied%20on%20the%20net%20to%20be%20connected%20for%20their%20daily%20needs%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20thrown%20out%20of%20gear.%20The%20administration%20always%20takes%20refuge%20under%20the%20facade%20that%20imposing%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20revoking%20the%20net%20can%20bring%20normalcy%20to%20a%20violence-hit%20area.%20Never%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20have%20such%20quick%20fixes%20worked%2C%20and%20they%20have%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20rather%20counterproductive.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20evil%20whispers%20have%20been%20burgeoning%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20internet%20has%20made%20the%20state%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20fake%20news%20and%20false%20propaganda.%20The%20administration%20never%20realises%20that%20it%20is%20also%20an%20eventual%20victim%20of%20its%20own%20ill-conceived%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrudent%20use%20of%20the%20internet%20would%20have%20easily%20provided%20channels%20to%20disseminate%20information%20useful%20to%20obliterate%20misgivings%20and%20to%20clear%20the%20air.%20Ironically%2C%20administrations%20have%20never%20bothered%20to%20assess%20the%20catastrophic%20impact%2C%20let%20alone%20analyse%20the%20economic%20loss.%20Industry%20sources%20have%20made%20a%20conservative%20estimate%20of%20loss%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20during%20the%20last%20three%20years%20on%20account%20of%20more%20than%2016%2C000%20hours%20of%20internet%20shutdowns%20across%20the%20country.%20But%20the%20impact%20is%20pervasive%20and%20extends%20well%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20economics%20and%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20affect%20even%20daily%2C%20mundane%20activities.%20The%20loss%20of%20business%20is%20tangible%2C%20but%20the%20devastating%20impact%20on%20education%2C%20information%2C%20health%2C%20entertainment%20and%20other%20facets%20of%20life%20do%20not%20find%20any%20mention%20at%20all%20in%20official%20reports.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20harping%20on%20about%20its%20achievements%20in%20turning%20India%20into%20a%20huge%20digital%20hub%2C%20but%20it%20also%20uses%20suspension%20of%20internet%20as%20the%20quickest%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20writer%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Communications%20and%20Information%20Technology%20that%20had%20deliberated%20at%20length%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20frequent%20internet%20shutdowns.%20On%20December%201%2C%202021%2C%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20presented%20to%20Parliament%20its%20report%20on%20%E2%80%9CSuspension%20of%20telecom%20services%2Finternet%20and%20its%20impact%E2%80%9D%20and%20recommended%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20measures%20including%20regulatory%20overhaul%2C%20oversight%20mechanisms%2C%20transparency%20and%20the%20need%20for%20consultation%20with%20stakeholders.%20But%20the%20departments%20have%20exhibited%20a%20lacklustre%20attitude%20in%20implementing%20these%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standing%20committee%20was%20aghast%20to%20know%20that%20none%20of%20the%20ministries%20have%20accounts%20of%20internet%20shut%20downs%20frequently%20happening%20at%20different%20places%20across%20the%20country.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20despite%20having%20a%20new%20Temporary%20Suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20and%20Public%20Safety%20Rules%2C%202017)%2C%20shutdowns%20are%20also%20being%20effected%20under%20Section%20144%20CrPC%2C%20which%20only%20require%20approval%20from%20an%20officer%20as%20low%20as%20a%20Tehsildar.%20The%20Telecom%20Rules%20issued%20in%202017%20made%20no%20reference%20to%20Section%20144%20CrPC%2C%20leading%20to%20such%20a%20conundrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20while%20expressing%20its%20displeasure%20over%20the%20negative%20attitude%20of%20the%20departments%20in%20implementing%20its%20earlier%20recommendations%2C%20tabled%20its%20Action%20Taken%20Report%20on%20February%209%2C%202023%20in%20Parliament.%20Recommendations%20included%20having%20a%20due%20process%20for%20invoking%20shutdowns%2C%20having%20a%20review%20committee%20with%20eminent%20persons%20including%20judges%20as%20members%2C%20drawing%20up%20uniform%20set%20of%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20and%20guidelines%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%20maintaining%20a%20centralised%20database%20for%20such%20internet%20shutdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Standing%20Committee%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20various%20high%20courts%20have%20detailed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20came%20up%20with%20directions%20and%20instructions%20in%20a%20catena%20of%20judgments.%20In%20September%202019%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsflc.in%2Fkerala-high-court-declares-right-access-internet-fundamental-right%2F%5C%22%3EKerala%20high%20court%20in%20a%20landmark%20decision%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20right%20to%20internet%20access%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20The%20court%20interpreted%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20right%20to%20internet%20to%20various%20fundamental%20rights%20including%20the%20right%20to%20education%2C%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20etc.%20In%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgment%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20detailed%20guidelines%20and%20categorically%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20practice%20any%20profession%20or%20carry%20on%20any%20trade%2C%20business%20or%20occupation%20over%20the%20medium%20of%20the%20internet%20enjoys%20constitutional%20protection%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20and%20Article%2019(1)(g)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20But%20every%20bit%20of%20it%20has%20been%20flouted%20by%20various%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdministrations%20may%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20suspension%20of%20internet%20services%20in%20certain%20scenarios%2C%20but%20it%20should%20not%20be%20done%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat.%20As%20the%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20suggested%2C%20it%20should%20be%20proportionate%20and%20should%20be%20done%20after%20carefully%20analysing%20the%20pros%20and%20cons.%20As%20a%20young%20entrepreneur%20in%20Imphal%20complained%20to%20me%2C%20he%20has%20been%20dragged%20into%20a%20dark%20cave%20due%20to%20the%20internet%20shutdown.%20We%20have%20no%20right%20to%20push%20our%20citizens%20to%20a%20pre-information%20era%20when%20the%20world%20has%20accepted%20internet%20as%20a%20basic%20human%20right.%20As%20the%20adage%20goes%2C%20%E2%80%9CSunlight%20is%20the%20best%20disinfectant%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20internet%20can%20play%20a%20constructive%20role%20in%20quelling%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%20Brittas%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20and%20recently%20visited%20Manipur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689332315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F15092828%2Finternet_cables001-1200x507-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fmanipur-is-further-proof-that-internet-shutdowns-do-more-harm-than-good%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20clueless%20government%20in%20Manipur%20has%20resorted%20to%20a%20sweeping%20inte