er%20life%20to%20save%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20Y%20K%2C%20the%20deputy%20conservator%20of%20forests%20(DCF)%20of%20Mangaluru%20division%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20on%20several%20missions%20with%20Meghana%20says%20the%20same.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20very%20light-footed%20and%20quick-witted%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20work.%20She%20does%20not%20even%20blink%20before%20jumping%20into%20wells%20and%20climbing%20floors%20of%20buildings%20to%20save%20the%20animal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%2020%20feet%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20that%20was%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Meghana%20Pemmaiah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20forest%20department%20is%20always%20short%20of%20such%20rescuers%20and%20Meghana%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20has%20been%20helping%20us%