ere%20students%20can%20understand%20where%20the%20food%20they%20consume%20comes%20from%2C%20while%20also%20helping%20take%20care%20of%20the%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20had%20a%20channel%20of%20water%20running%20through%20it%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20restore%20it.%20The%20school%20also%20has%20a%20plantation%20area%20where%20they%20grow%20their%20food%20and%20the%20produce%20is%20utilised%20in%20the%20cafeteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20also%20has%20a%20very%20unique%20play%20area%20on%20the%20terrace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20building%20was%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20the%20terrace%20of%20the%20building%20comes%20at%20par%20with%20the%20treetops.%20The%20terrace%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%20with%20leaves%20peeking%20out%20of%20punctures%20in%20the%20floorplate%2C%20allowing%20children%20the%20opportunity%20to%20play%20among%20the%20treetops%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akanksha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20are%20free%20to%20climb%20the%20trees%20and%20pluck%20the%20produce%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gives%20them%20a%20space%20to%20live%20a%20childhood%20that%20is%20much%20more%20than%20just%20gadgets%20and%20television.%20The%20environment%20that%20they%20might%20see%20on%20screens%20is%20a%20reality%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saurabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20sustainability%20out%20of%20textbooks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20building%20complements%20and%20blends%20into%20the%20greenery%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%20the%20building%20materials%20sing%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CPreserving%20the%20existing%20nature%20was%20one%20of%20our%20first%20goals%20while%20designing%20the%20property.%20There%20were%20fruit%20trees%20such%20as%20mango%20and%20jamun%2C%20which%20are%20still%20growing%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20mate